00:01:36.770 --> 00:01:39.280
DAVID THORBURN: And compare
this-- think about this scene

00:01:39.280 --> 00:01:42.860
and then compare t-- to the
opening scene of The 400 Blows

00:01:42.860 --> 00:01:45.120
and you'll feel a
difference in mood, I think.

00:01:45.120 --> 00:01:47.390
Even the music is a part of it.

00:01:47.390 --> 00:01:49.910
So he's in great despair
here, and we in the audience

00:01:49.910 --> 00:01:50.610
know that.

